## And

---



[Meta Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/meta_condition_types/and)

Checks whether all of the provided conditions are fulfilled.

Type ID: `origins:and`




---

### Examples

```json
"condition": {
    "type": "origins:and",
    "conditions": [
        {
            "type": "origins:daytime"
        },
        {      
            "type": "origins:invisible"
        }
    ]
}
```

This example will check if it is both daytime, and the entity is invisible.

